2004-02-12

	GNU mpq-tools 0.3.0 was released.

2004-02-12   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* FAQ: updated the example with information about
	  libmpq_listfile_open()

	* README: updated for the new functions

	* configure.ac: added db/Makefile and db/diablo2/Makefile target,
	  updated libmpq version information

	* Makefile.am: added new subdir db to target

	* TODO: added error handling to TODO

	* libmpq/mpq.c: added function libmpq_file_number(),
	  libmpq_file_check(), libmpq_listfile_open() and
	  libmpq_listfile_close()

	* libmpq/parser.c: added function libmpq_conf_parse_line() and
	  libmpq_conf_get_array()

	* libmpq/mpq.h: - added LIBMPQ_FILE_TYPE_INT and
	  LIBMPQ_FILE_TYPE_CHAR to define which type a file has - added
	  LIBMPQ_CONF_EFILE_OPEN, LIBMPQ_CONF_EFILE_CORRUPT,
	  LIBMPQ_CONF_EFILE_LIST_CORRUPT, LIBMPQ_CONF_EFILE_NOT_FOUND and
	  LIBMPQ_CONF_EFILE_VERSION - exported all new library functions.

	* libmpq/common.c: added function libmpq_read_listfile() to parse
	  list database file and removed no longer needed
	  libmpq_get_listfile()

	* libmpq/common.h: renamed LIBMPQ_CONF_EVALUE to
	  LIBMPQ_CONF_EVALUE_NOT_FOUND

	* src/Makefile.am: added -DLIBMPQ_LISTDB_PATH to CFLAGS

	* src/mpq-extract.c: - added function mpq_extract_file_extract() to
	  extract files from mpq archive - added support for using internal
	  listfile database or specific listfile - added support for
	  namebased and numberbased extraction - added support for
	  extracting specific file

	* src/mpq-extract.h: added members listfile, number, file and
	  filename to the mpq_extract_options_s structure

	* src/mpq-info.h: increased patchlevel to 1 :)

	* src/mpq-info.c: removed mpq_a->header memory allocation because
	  it is not needed

	* db/: diablo2/Makefile.am, Makefile.am: initial checkin

	* db/diablo2/setup.mpq.conf: changed names again for final release
	  of libmpq 0.3.0

2004-01-31   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* libmpq/common.h: merged with parser.h

	* libmpq/parser.c: renamed some defines

	* libmpq/common.c: renamed some defines

	* src/mpq-extract.c: added libmpq_get_listfile()

	* libmpq/parser.h: merged with common.h

	* libmpq/common.c: small bugfixes

	* libmpq/parser.c: fixed int return

	* libmpq/common.c: added union for the return values

	* libmpq/parser.c: added types to libmpq_conf_get_value()

	* libmpq/parser.h: initial checkin

	* db/diablo2/setup.mpq.conf: version 2 of config file

	* libmpq/parser.c: initial checkin

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: added parser.c

	* libmpq/common.c: changed the complete libmpq_get_listfile_rec()
	  function

	* libmpq/common.h: added some new defines

	* libmpq/mpq.c: changed listfile detection

	* libmpq/mpq.h: file descriptor in mpq_list is not needed

2004-01-29   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* libmpq/common.c: replaced a strcmp() with strncmp()

	* libmpq/common.c: added function libmpq_free_listfile() to free
	  memory used for getting all listdb files and
	  libmpq_get_listfile_rec() to return a record from listdb
	  directory

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: added common.h to noinst_HEADERS

	* libmpq/common.h: initial checkin

2004-01-28   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* libmpq/mpq.c: fixed a misunderstanding comment :)

	* libmpq/mpq.h: added members mpq_name, mpq_type, mpq_game and
	  mpq_game_version to struct mpq_list

	* libmpq/common.c: added function libmpq_get_listfile() to retrieve
	  filelist of available listfiles

	* src/: mpq-info.h, mpq-extract.h: added some #ifndef for header
	  already included

2004-01-24   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* src/mpq-extract.c: updated for use of libmpq_file_name()

	* libmpq/common.c: added function libmpq_detect_listfile() which
	  reads some file information and decide which listfile should be
	  used

	* libmpq/mpq.h: added filename member to mpq_file.

	* libmpq/mpq.c: added function libmpq_file_name() to retrieve
	  filename by given number

2004-01-23   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* src/mpq-extract.c: maybe a broken td tag :)

	* src/mpq-extract.c: added the id tag

	* libmpq/mpq.h: added new defines used by libmpq_file_info()

	* libmpq/mpq.c: added the libmpq_file_info() function to get some
	  useful information about a file inside an archive

	* src/mpq-extract.c: added the file information for compressed and
	  uncompressed size and the compression type

	* TODO: added the job for bruting all unknown filenames in
	  blizzards mpq archives

2004-01-22   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* db/diablo2/setup.mpq.conf: added the rest of the known files for
	  that archive

2004-01-21   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* db/diablo2/setup.mpq.conf: added new files to the german filelist

	* src/mpq-extract.c: massive rewrite for use with listfile support
	  in libmpq-0.3.0

	* src/mpq-extract.h: added commandline option structure

	* libmpq/common.c: removed all external library functions

	* libmpq/mpq.c: all functions, developer should use stay now here

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: updated for mpq.c

	* db/diablo2/setup.mpq.conf: initial checkin

2004-01-17

	GNU mpq-tools 0.2.1 was released.

2004-01-17   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: fixed for installing the mpq.h

	* AUTHORS, COPYING, FAQ, INSTALL, README, THANKS, TODO: initial
	  checkin for first public release

	* src/: mpq-extract.c, mpq-info.c: upgraded for common naming
	  scheme

	* libmpq/: common.c, explode.c, explode.h, extract.c, huffman.c,
	  mpq.h, wave.c, wave.h: upgraded for common naming scheme

2004-01-16   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: added noinst_HEADERS

	* configure.ac: disable default built of shared libraries

	* src/Makefile.am: some better dependency handling

	* src/mpq-extract.h: initial checkin with default defines for
	  mpq-extract.c

	* src/mpq-extract.c: first usable command line version for
	  extracting

	* src/mpq-info.c: changed some defines to fit the naming scheme

	* src/mpq-info.h: changed some defines to fit the naming scheme

2004-01-09   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: libmpq would be installed from now on

	* configure.ac: libmpq would be installed from now on

	* src/: mpq-info.c, mpq-info.h: verbose mode removed because it is
	  not needed for that small utility

2004-01-07   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* configure.ac: added zlib check and ability to disable zlib.

	* src/mpq-info.c: added functions to get mpq archive informations.

	* src/mpq-info.h: added structure which saves the command line
	  arguments for later use

	* src/mpq-extract.c: updated to only extract files from archive,
	  nothing more or less

	* src/Makefile.am: removed mpq-common.c from build rules.

	* src/mpq-common.c: common functions moved to libmpq/common.c

	* src/Makefile.am: updated for mpq-info.c and mpq-info.h

	* libmpq/: wave.c, wave.h: functions for wave file decompression
	  used by blizzard in storm.dll

	* libmpq/: huffman.c, huffman.h: functions for the huffman
	  decompression used by blizzard in storm.dll

	* libmpq/explode.h: added structures for the PKWARE decompression
	  routines

	* libmpq/common.c: common functions used and exported with libmpq

	* libmpq/extract.c: added wave, zlib and huffman decompression
	  functions.

	* libmpq/explode.c: changed copyright and removed no longer needed
	  include files.

	* libmpq/Makefile.am: updated for new source files.

	* libmpq/mpq.h: updated for wave, zlib and huffman decompression

	* libmpq/mpqpkzip.h: no longer needed, because moved to explode.h

2003-12-03   Maik Broemme <mbroemme@plusserver.de>

	* src/mpq-tools.h: mpq-tools.h moved to libmpq and named mpq.h

	* libmpq/mpq.h: old mpq-tools.h renamed to mpq.h and put to libmpq,
	  also some updates fpr the PKWARE compression.

	* libmpq/: explode.c, extract.c, mpqpkzip.h: initial checkin for
	  libmpq library

	* Makefile.am, configure.ac, src/Makefile.am, src/mpq-common.c,
	  src/mpq-extract.c: All files updated for seperate libmpq and
	  PKWARE data compression

